{"nodes": [{"id": "docs_volumes_21_security", "label": "Security Architecture (Volume 21)", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "docs/volumes/21-Security.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_volumes_21_security_threat_model", "label": "Threat Model", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/volumes/21-Security.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Five threat actors: legitimate user, file-access attacker, network attacker, malicious plugin, compromised AI provider. Four asset categories: API keys, SQLite databases, source/translation files, logs."}, {"id": "docs_volumes_21_security_electron_sandbox", "label": "Electron Sandbox Configuration", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/volumes/21-Security.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "BrowserWindow with sandbox:true, contextIsolation:true, nodeIntegration:false, allowRunningInsecureContent:false, webSecurity:true. No app.enableSandbox(). This is the Electron 12+ security baseline."}, {"id": "docs_volumes_21_security_path_traversal", "label": "Path Traversal Prevention", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/volumes/21-Security.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "assertWithinProject(basePath, targetPath) validates all file paths. Resolves with path.resolve, verifies against authorized project directory. Rejects direct traversal (../), encoded traversal (%2e%2e), symlinks outside project, absolute paths, mixed separators on Windows."}, {"id": "docs_volumes_21_security_api_key_storage", "label": "API Key Storage Strategy", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/volumes/21-Security.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Tiered approach: Primary: keytar (OS keychain: Windows Credential Locker, macOS Keychain, Linux libsecret). Fallback: AES-256-GCM encrypted file at ~/.noveltrad/secrets.json. Keys never logged, never sent to renderer, never exposed to plugins. UI shows masked value (sk-...XXXX)."}, {"id": "docs_volumes_21_security_csp", "label": "Content Security Policy", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/volumes/21-Security.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Strict CSP via session.defaultSession.webRequest.onHeadersReceived: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; img-src 'self' data:."}, {"id": "keytar", "label": "keytar (OS Keychain)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/volumes/21-Security.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}], "edges": [{"source": "docs_volumes_21_security_electron_sandbox", "target": "electron_electron", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/volumes/21-Security.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "docs_volumes_21_security_api_key_storage", "target": "keytar", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/volumes/21-Security.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "docs_volumes_21_security_path_traversal", "target": "docs_volumes_16_internal_api_zod_validation", "relation": "conceptually_related_to", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.75, "source_file": "docs/volumes/21-Security.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "docs_volumes_21_security_electron_sandbox", "target": "docs_volumes_16_internal_api_preload_script", "relation": "conceptually_related_to", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file":